---
title: Get Your Greens Rice Bowl with Bok Choy, Edamame, Asparagus, and Wasabi Crema
description: Every element of this recipe brings something to feel good about: fiber-rich brown rice provides the base, while asparagus and bok choy add their vitamin-rich green veggie flair. Edamame has minerals like iron and magnesium, and cashews are a good source of healthy, unsaturated fats. Even the wasabi crema on top, with its prickly, peppery kick, will wake your senses and make you feel invigorated, energized, and pumped up.
